biography: Lauri, a name synonymous with dedication at Jyväs-Golf, is known for his meticulous approach to the game. While he might appear reserved on the surface, those who know him well understand his playful nature.

Lauri has appeared once at the Hector Trophée. While he has never lifted the coveted trophy nor claimed the Victor Trophy, his impact on the tournament has been undeniable. Though considered retired from Hector events, his presence is missed, and the possibility of a future return always lingers in the air.
